{
  "stem": "10699.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had sometimes to run from the lorry, and run into the forest, the nearest place where we could hide, and then go back again.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time we reached that little village, the Germans had-- had reached our-- our place and were going forward towards Vichy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, we-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the commandant of the-- in that village said that all men aged from 18 to 45 should go to Vichy to be recruited.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the people-- I was very ill at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had caught tonsillitis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but we had to go on to Vichy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we arrived in Vichy, somehow nobody found the place where you're supposed to be recruited, so we just watched what was going on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the Germans had reached, now, Vichy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were emptying the shops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, all the lovely-- the goods that they could find, either they took it or they paid for it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were-- they were buying, or they were looting, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we could see that wasn't the place to stay, because they were all in Vichy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father decided that we should really continue, and we shouldn't stay in Vichy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And therefore, we-- we decided to go to the next town, which was probably also a similar town to the town where we lived, Sarreguemines, because it was a mining town, a working class town, where we probably could do business and work again.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went on to Saint-Etienne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But of course, the Germans had, by that time, also gone right from France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had looted-- by that time, they emptied the shops immediately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's only afterwards that there was-- they made a kind of accord with the Vichy government that France was separated, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were actually in free France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the rest of France was occupied, and we were called France Libre.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, we were under the Vichy government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in June, he brought out-- the Vichy government brought out the new laws against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Therefore, everybody had to register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At the [NON-ENGLISH], at the police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, where they lived, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where they came from.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were given ration cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But of course, our ration cards had always the name-- say Jew on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "J.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were known as-- that we were-- But everybody knew we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have a yellow star in free France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in the rest of France they wore a Star of David.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, at that point, took another apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we ran from Blamont, we ran so fast that we left all the valuable things behind, because we were in a panic.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So whatever my father said we should take, we took the wrong thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we only noticed that we were in the track halfway down France that we had really taken nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That we were nearly penniless, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of the things that we could have made money or got money from, we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we arrived in Saint-Etienne, we had to find somewhere to live that wasn't expensive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had, certainly, no money to buy things at the black market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So things were very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- we-- we had to find some kind of way to live again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How to make a living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father found, again, for me-- I was now 16 and 1/2, 17.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He again-- he found a job for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, I can't have only students.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to go and work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I will see what I can do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My brothers went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My older brother, David, he was finishing his matriculation, so he finished it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Armand went to school, to they called [NON-ENGLISH], and the younger one went to an ordinary school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we all had to-- and so we tried to live.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You felt that you-- perhaps you were hoping all the time that the day would come that it will finish the war, and you could go on with whatever you wanted to do, you know, to study.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somebody had to bring money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It seemed a shame that the one that was doing matriculation should stop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The others were too young to stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was only me that had to go out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's why I went to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
